query:
/*+  */ select count(account.display_name)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on tq1.question_id = q1.id AND q1.score > 10 AND q1.view_count < 1949
inner join tag AS t1
on tq1.tag_id = t1.id AND t1.name IN ('contracts',
'freelance-websites')
inner join so_user AS u1
on q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.site_id = u1.site_id
inner join site AS s1
on tq1.site_id = s1.site_id AND q1.site_id = s1.site_id AND t1.site_id = s1.site_id AND s1.site_name = 'freelancing'
inner join account AS account
on account.id = u1.account_id
inner join comment AS c1
on c1.site_id = q1.site_id AND c1.post_id = q1.id;
